        "ghargharkali"
      ],
      "post_text": "Today's name is Shhmashhana kalika. The dark-bodied Goddess of the cremation ground, the power of death and dissolution. Jai Ma. #ghargharkali"
    },
    {
      "queue_index": 2,
      "source_index": 2,
      "post_id": "814766726962118656",
      "post_url": "https://kakakaforadyakali.tumblr.com/post/814766726962118656",
      "posted_at": "2026-04-24T09:15:01.582675+00:00",
      "text_hash": "90dafb2182fbd7d875f0bc544727473dc83288263a52fe2801bc6ed25af94abd",
      "tags": [
        "ghargharkali"
      ],
      "post_text": "Today's name is Kali. The Black Goddess, ruler of Time. Jai Ma. #ghargharkali"
    },
    {
      "queue_index": 3,
      "source_index": 3,
      "post_id": "814766799712305152",
      "post_url": "https://kakakaforadyakali.tumblr.com/post/814766799712305152",
      "posted_at": "2026-04-24T09:16:11.005279+00:00",
      "text_hash": "b11201e902877922dd084a61eaaa953f1caa5183e18545a1ba0a8b9b5c379286",
      "tags": [
        "ghargharkali"
      ],
      "post_text": "Today's name is Bhadra kali. The all-auspicious Dark Mother. Jai Ma. #ghargharkali"
    },
    {
      "queue_index": 4,
      "source_index": 4,
      "post_id": "814766947836248064",
      "post_url": "https://kakakaforadyakali.tumblr.com/post/814766947836248064",
      "posted_at": "2026-04-24T09:18:32.187080+00:00",
      "text_hash": "56d5fd427fc92382364dd0098195c515517609c2fdeabecb96539991031578ea",
      "tags": [
        "ghargharkali"
      ],
      "post_text": "Today's name is Kapalini. She who bears the skull, showing Her transcendence over mortality and the cycle of creation. Jai Ma. #ghargharkali"
    },
    {
      "queue_index": 5,
      "source_index": 5,
      "post_id": "814770374806061056",
      "post_url": "https://kakakaforadyakali.tumblr.com/post/814770374806061056",
      "posted_at": "2026-04-24T10:13:00.415367+00:00",
      "text_hash": "95e4ee6dc2d77f343c485f9688fc36b5e7f765a161282673e1f69c979e88903c",
      "tags": [
        "ghargharkali"
      ],
      "post_text": "Today's name is Guhya kali. The hidden and secret Dark Goddess. Jai Ma. #ghargharkali"
    },
    {
      "queue_index": 6,
      "source_index": 6,
      "post_id": "814772529677877248",
      "post_url": "https://kakakaforadyakali.tumblr.com/post/814772529677877248",
      "posted_at": "2026-04-24T10:47:15.522075+00:00",
      "text_hash": "b8b796e6c9e28373b7824ce6abecb9b04bce7271ac4dc1afa9838aa338f47ca8",
      "tags": [
        "ghargharkali"
      ],
      "post_text": "Today's name is Maha-kali. The Great Dark Mother, beautiful and compassionate to devotees, yet terrifying to their enemies. Jai Ma. #ghargharkali"
    },
    {
      "queue_index": 7,
      "source_index": 7,
      "post_id": "814775871450824704",
      "post_url": "https://kakakaforadyakali.tumblr.com/post/814775871450824704",
      "posted_at": "2026-04-24T11:40:22.404418+00:00",
      "text_hash": "f18872c50d3f400a39222ae4444547c8a15ed051cf15b3fb0610d5a0c0e87570",
      "tags": [
        "ghargharkali"
      ],
      "post_text": "Today's name is Kurukulla-'virodhini. The destroyer of opposition, especially as the one who bestows siddhis and protects those who attain them. Jai Ma. #ghargharkali"
    },
    {
      "queue_index": 8,
      "source_index": 8,
      "post_id": "814777384819736576",
      "post_url": "https://kakakaforadyakali.tumblr.com/post/814777384819736576",
      "posted_at": "2026-04-24T12:04:25.702749+00:00",
      "text_hash": "ef6dbbc4e80fac6e5c61a8129d9202f820a812e7e7bbdecd8ea2c068b5ff2344",
      "tags": [
        "ghargharkali"
      ],
      "post_text": "Today's name is Kalika. The tender form of Kali, the Dark One, gentle in presence yet potent in power. Jai Ma. #ghargharkali"
    },
    {
      "queue_index": 9,
      "source_index": 9,
      "post_id": "814779595930927104",
      "post_url": "https://kakakaforadyakali.tumblr.com/post/814779595930927104",
      "posted_at": "2026-04-24T12:39:34.364154+00:00",
      "text_hash": "14da8638e51cc428a80279b454a7482965617e551173fd2e0642aeb08cecfbb1",
      "tags": [
        "ghargharkali"
      ],
      "post_text": "Today's name is Kala ratri cha. She who is the Dark Night of Time, the profound dissolution and ultimate reality beyond all manifestations. Jai Ma. #ghargharkali"
    },
    {
      "queue_index": 10,
      "source_index": 10,
      "post_id": "814781608631631872",
      "post_url": "https://kakakaforadyakali.tumblr.com/post/814781608631631872",
      "posted_at": "2026-04-24T13:11:33.918244+00:00",
      "text_hash": "ea7dd2778070f5dd4d436a617a8e5ed9d758f7714a814d0435fa6cc320167a1d",
      "tags": [
        "ghargharkali"
      ],
      "post_text": "Today's name is Maha-kala nitambini. The dark-limbed one who rests upon Mahakala, the great Lord of Time. Jai Ma. #ghargharkali"
    },
    {
      "queue_index": 11,
      "source_index": 11,
      "post_id": "814784310832939008",
      "post_url": "https://kakakaforadyakali.tumblr.com/post/814784310832939008",
      "posted_at": "2026-04-24T13:54:30.973948+00:00",
      "text_hash": "661a438d5bbe47e04346645b6524ed582056cfed9ff79736a19a6eaf124ba056",
      "tags": [
        "ghargharkali"
      ],
      "post_text": "Today's name is Kala bhairava bharya cha. The consort of Kala Bhairava. Jai Ma. #ghargharkali"
    },
    {
      "queue_index": 12,
      "source_index": 12,
      "post_id": "814787762461032448",
      "post_url": "https://kakakaforadyakali.tumblr.com/post/814787762461032448",
      "posted_at": "2026-04-24T14:49:22.643002+00:00",
      "text_hash": "9724f38341ede114319703792acc5a9168db68cce81a0fcdd47bd11f77d33ede",
      "tags": [
        "ghargharkali"
      ],
      "post_text": "Today's name is Kula vartma prakashhini. The illuminator of the path of the spiritual lineage, revealing the essence of the Kaula tradition. Jai Ma. #ghargharkali"
    }
